hobbit (4.2.0.dfsg-6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Remove /usr/lib/hobbit/*/tmp/ symlinks, set BBTMP="/var/lib/hobbit/tmp".
    (Closes: #446982)
  * Drop "hobbit" binary again, instead bbcmd will set PATH to include
    the hobbit binaries.
